the earlier "Event binding" section for more details.</fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">Finally, when the view itself is disposed of with <fo:inline font-family="monospace" font-size="10pt">leave()</fo:inline>, it
