}</fo:block><fo:block space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">This is a function that calls <fo:inline font-family="monospace" font-size="10pt">inherits</fo:inline> to make a new subclass.  The comments
